QuestData.Title: Lay of the Land[TEMP]
QuestData.Description: Grah!!$b$bFor every one of these muck-flingers we kill, another two spring from the woods to take its place. I wouldn't share this with the others, but it's clear that we won't last long here, $n.$b$bI must stay and defend what remains of our belongings. You scout out the region and seek a solution to our primate problem.$b$bGo now. Our hope goes with you...
